Paul Monk from Essex was wanted by Spanish police for questioning over the kidnap and murder of Francis Brennan . 
  His body washed up on a Costa Blanca beach in March last year . 
  Monk was on the UK's most wanted list on suspicion of drug trafficking . 
  He was also wanted by the Metropolitan Police on drug offences . 
  Spanish police arrested him in a dramatic raid on his villa in Alicante . 
 